    • Constructor Detail

      • Event

        public Event(EventType type,
             @Nullable
             Alarm alarm,
             @Nullable
             AlarmAttendant attendant,
             @Nullable
             Patient patient)
        Creates an Event with optional arguments. Not all events are directly Alarm related, thus AlarmAttendant and Patient parameters need to be available for these (rare) cases.
        Parameters:
        type - EventType as specified in the EventType enum
        alarm - An Alarm object (can be null)
        attendant - An AlarmAttendant object (can be null)
        patient - A Patient object (can be null)
